Author: neuroticflowerchild
Text: Also forgot to mention that I've been doing this pretty much on my own because my family doesn't know about my ed and my bf doesn't understand it and I'm not seeing a psychologist anymore.. I see my doctor like once a month or less and same with my nutritionist and they let me do pretty much whatever the fuck I want in the end. Might be because I'm an adult and can't be forced to treatment and I'm in a decent shape anyway so there's no need for that. I'm just kinda sad that I have to do this recovery thing pretty much alone if I want to because there's no one pushing me forwards except my nutritionist and doctor like once a month for 45min.. that motivation doesn't last too long..
